These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
House: modern, victorian
City: prague, new-york
1. City:prague is in an even position##4
2. City:new-york == House:victorian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| House   | victorian | modern |
| City     | new-york    | prague   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Color: lavender, amber
Movie-Genre: action, comedy
1. Movie-Genre:action is in an odd position##4
2. Color:amber is on the left of Color:lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Color   | amber | lavender        |
| Movie-Genre      | action  | comedy |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Color: azure, lilac
House: modern, craftsman
1. House:modern is in an odd position##4
2. Color:lilac is on the left of Color:azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Color   | lilac    | azure |
| House   | modern | craftsman |

